He <@U0786JB94US> - this needs to be done via CSS.

Something like
```.blog-card{
background-color:#ffffff
}
.blog-card:hover{
background-color: #eeeeee
}```
If you'd like to use existing colors from your theme you can do it like this:
```.blog-card{
background-color:{{ path.to.color.variable }}
}
.blog-card:hover{
background-color: {{ path.to.different.color.variable }}
}```
you can write me a DM; I'll guide you through
